Potential health gains and health losses in eleven EU countries attainable 
through feasible prevalences of the life-style related risk factors alcohol, 
BMI, and smoking: a quantitative health impact assessment.

Lhachimi SK(1)(2)(3)(4), Nusselder WJ(5), Smit HA(6)(7), Baili P(8), Bennett 
K(9), Fernández E(10)(11), Kulik MC(5)(7), Lobstein T(12), Pomerleau J(13), 
