(10)Tobacco Control Unit, Institut Català d'Oncologia-IDIBELL, L'Hospitalet de 
Llobregat Barcelona, Barcelona, Spain.
(11)Department of Clinical Sciences, School of Medicine, Campus of Bellvitge, 
