Design and protocol for the Focusing on Clozapine Unresponsive Symptoms (FOCUS) 
trial: a randomised controlled trial.

Pyle M(1)(2), Norrie J(3), Schwannauer M(4), Kingdon D(5), Gumley A(6), 
