Prostate-Specific Antigen: Nonspecific in Deceased Organ Donors.

Pabisiak K(1), Ostrowski M(2), Kram A(3), Safranow K(4), Myślak M(5), Sieńko 
J(2), Sulikowski T(2), Ciechanowski K(5).

Author information:
